_sText:
Remake of Killhouse map from Call of Duty 4.

I loved this map so I remade it for Counter Strike: Source, hopefully will be good fun in GunGame and people practicing their aim. 

It has HDR lighting, some good details (tried to make it as close to COD4's version as possible), and also custom soundscapes for that extra touch!

Buyzones are on each side of the map where teams spawn, and this map is fully compatible with bots.
Enjoy!
